11
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:02,270
You should

12
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,520
interact more often.

13
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:06,320
Shaocheng,

14
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:07,990
it seems

15
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,640
you will soon have a father-in-law.

16
