Corydalis Yanhusuo, Horse Bezoar]

17
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:36,520
[Help the People]

18
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:44,670
[Anxin House]

19
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:53,320
You are...?

20
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:08,000
You're doing pretty well.

21
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:13,520
How can I help you?

22
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,440
My heart is troubled,

23
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,910
but alas, no one can help.

24
00:05:26,910 --> 00:05:28,640
Why don't you tell me about it first?

25
00:05:33,910 --> 00:05:35,080
Over ten years ago,

26
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:37,470
it was you who caused this trouble.

27
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,030
Can you fix it?

28
00:05:56,350 --> 00:05:57,910
I'll never forget that day.

29
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:00,830
I met

30
00:06:00,910 --> 00:06:02,590
a sweet and innocent little girl,

31
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,910
but she

32
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,000
led me straight into the abyss.

33
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,680
Do you know the despair I felt,

34
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,080
locked in that abandoned house?

35
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:11,440
Do you know how those monsters

36
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,440
tortured me

37
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:13,390
over and over again?

38
00:06:13,710 --> 00:06:14,790
And that fire

39
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,560
filled the air

40
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:20,310
with the smell of burning human flesh.

41
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,640
If I hadn't been locked

42
00:06:21,710 --> 00:06:22,760
in the last room,

43
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:23,880
lucky enough

44
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,000
to find a way out,

45
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,120
I would also have been burned alive.

46
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,440
I endured excruciating pain

47
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,880
just to survive.

48
00:06:33,590 --> 00:06:35,030
Now, looking at myself,

49
00:06:35,150 --> 00:06:36,960
I feel nothing but disgust.

50
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:39,000
It wasn't until I saw

51
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,590
the Censor case announcement

52
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:44,320
that I realized

53
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,520
you were the girl

54
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,590
from back then.

55
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,320
You've become

56
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:54,150
a renowned psychiatrist.

57
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,640
You live such a good life

58
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,880
while I've had mine destroyed,

59
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:06,320
living like some horrendous ghost.

60
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,270
Why?

61
00:07:07,790 --> 00:07:09,150
As long as you're alive,

62
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:10,590
I'll continue to suffer.

63
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,640
Why are you still alive?

64
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,760
Why don't you just die?

65
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:25,670
[Anxin House]

66
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,350
Ping'an,

67
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:52,590
what happened to you?

68
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,640
It's nothing.

69
00:07:58,230 --> 00:07:59,680
I just didn't sleep well last night.

70
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,790
So cold.

71
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,120
Well then,

72
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,030
I'll make you

73
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,350
some tonic soup to boost your energy.

74
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,880
You'd better drink it all.

75
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:10,640
All right,

76
00:08:11,470 --> 00:08:12,680
I'll drink it all.

77
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,000
So,

78
00:08:20,350 --> 00:08:22,710
have you decided
what you'll do in the future?

79
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:26,680
I still love singing.

80
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:29,830
In the future,
I plan to write my own songs

81
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,200
and live a carefree life.

82
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:33,160
Sure.

83
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,800
Shaocheng

84
00:08:37,470 --> 00:08:39,080
is a reliable person
who can get things done.

85
00:08:40,590 --> 00:08:41,280
Mr. Yao,

86
00:08:41,710 --> 00:08:42,400
be sure

87
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:43,680
to take care of him in the future.

88
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,590
Allow me
to make a toast to you, Mr. Yao.

89
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,440
Since

90
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,320
you're so highly regarded
by the Prince of Kangping

91
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,440
and favored by Miss Wu,

92
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,280
you must have
some exceptional qualities.

93
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,510
Perhaps one day,

94
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,400
we'll turn to you for guidance.

95
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,200
I'm truly flattered.

96
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,710
Shaocheng is a man of great potential,

97
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:05,800
destined for greatness.

98
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:06,750
So,

99
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:07,800
please allow us

100
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:09,920
to congratulate you in advance, sir.

101
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,710
[Kangping Mansion]

102
00:09:14,710 --> 00:09:15,160
Sirs,

103
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:16,750
please take care.

104
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:18,400
All right, Shaocheng.

105
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:18,870
Please go back now.

106
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:19,350
Go back.

107
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,040
Xian'er,

108
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,230
tomorrow is your mother's birthday.

109
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:26,440
Bring the rock sugar cakes

110
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:27,830
and go visit her

111
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,080
with Shaocheng.

112
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,920
I've been tied up with work lately

113
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:31,960
and don't have the time.

114
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:33,960
Sir, do you know

115
00:09:34,630 --> 00:09:35,680
that Xian'er

116
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:36,990
also loves rock sugar cakes?

117
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,200
She didn't have a taste for sweets
when she was a child,

118
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,080
but that's changed now.

119
00:09:42,350 --> 00:09:42,990
Perhaps

120
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,560
it's because she's

121
00:09:44,990 --> 00:09:45,990
thinking of her mother.

122
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:47,470
I see.

123
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:49,160
There are things

124
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,870
in this world even you

125
00:09:50,870 --> 00:09:51,630
are unwilling to face.

126
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:54,870
I didn't expect you

127
00:09:55,710 --> 00:09:57,440
to be so thoughtful.

128
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,040
I'm sure my mother

129
00:09:59,590 --> 00:10:00,710
will be pleased tomorrow.

130
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,160
You two really get along well.

131
00:10:03,990 --> 00:10:04,990
His one word

132
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,400
outweighs hundreds of mine.

133
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:16,900
[Anxin House]

134
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:52,890
I never imagined

135
00:12:53,490 --> 00:12:54,890
the noble Princess of Kangping
would live

136
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,490
in such a humble temple

137
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,650
in the mountains.

138
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:58,580
What?

139
00:12:58,940 --> 00:12:59,610
Is it so strange to you?

140
00:13:00,770 --> 00:13:01,980
What's truly surprising
is that the Vice Minister

141
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:02,820
of the Court of Judicial Review

142
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:04,460
comes from the Mang Gutter.

143
00:13:07,460 --> 00:13:08,460
Then why would you

144
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:09,460
marry me,

145
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:10,940
a man

146
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:12,940
from Mang Gutter?

147
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:14,530
Marriage can simply be

148
00:13:14,770 --> 00:13:15,730
a deal for me,

149
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:17,180
as long as we are both happy.

150
00:13:17,530 --> 00:13:18,180
Minister Yuan,

151
00:13:19,340 --> 00:13:20,220
do you understand?

152
00:13:28,770 --> 00:13:30,870
[Wei Xuanmin, Master Suxuan]

153
00:13:36,370 --> 00:13:36,890
Mother.

154
00:13:42,650 --> 00:13:43,490
Master Suxuan.

155
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:51,940
I'm Shaocheng.

156
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:53,610
Greetings, Master Suxuan.

157
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:55,770
He is my future husband.

158
00:13:57,010 --> 00:13:57,610
You've never

159
00:13:58,220 --> 00:13:59,300
involved yourself in my affairs,

160
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:01,820
but I think I should bring him

161
00:14:02,610 --> 00:14:04,100
to meet you before we tie the knot.

162
00:14:05,650 --> 00:14:06,940
It's been so long since your last visit.

163
00:14:08,220 --> 00:14:10,420
Anything interesting happening
down the mountain recently?

164
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:11,650
Yes.

165
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:14,010
There's a dead tree
next to the Shangyang Palace.

166
00:14:14,370 --> 00:14:15,420
It's more than a century old.

167
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:17,850
The Ministry of Works
planned to remove it,

168
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:19,980
but to their surprise, it's sprouting

169
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,850
new buds in this late autumn.

170
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:23,220
They all say

171
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:24,650
it's a good omen.

172
00:14:26,650 --> 00:14:27,850
Do you know how trees

173
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,010
and people are alike?

174
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:35,420
A tree can sprout new buds

175
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:36,730
because its roots

176
00:14:36,820 --> 00:14:37,730
remain alive beneath the soil.

177
00:14:38,130 --> 00:14:38,850
The human heart

178
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:40,340
should be the same.

179
00:14:40,890 --> 00:14:42,010
If one goes against

180
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:43,420
their true nature,

181
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:45,220
they will soon wither,

182
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:46,370
just like a tree

183
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:47,530
without roots.

184
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:49,850
Fame and fortune are fleeting,

185
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:51,940
like the passing of days.

186
00:14:52,610 --> 00:14:53,580
Be it marriage

187
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:55,060
or anything else,

188
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:56,650
let your heart

189
00:14:57,650 --> 00:14:58,980
guide your choices.

190
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:01,890
I understand.

191
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:03,300
Since it's still early,

192
00:15:03,770 --> 00:15:05,250
let us share a meal with you
before we leave.

193
00:15:05,820 --> 00:15:06,490
No need.

194
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:08,460
The food here is simple,

195
00:15:08,530 --> 00:15:09,490
and it might not be to your taste.

196
00:15:10,980 --> 00:15:11,820
Just head down the mountain.

197
00:15:33,730 --> 00:15:34,180
Ping'an.

198
00:15:40,010 --> 00:15:40,490
Ping'an.

199
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:43,530
Perfect timing,

200
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:44,940
I want to tell you something.

201
00:15:57,890 --> 00:15:59,340
[Lease Agreement]
Isn't this the clinic's lease agreement?

202
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,010
Why are you showing it to me?

203
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,770
You've made plans for your future,

204
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:04,700
and I want a change as well.

205
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:06,700
I'm closing the clinic

206
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:08,300
and handing

207
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:09,340
the lease over to you.

208
00:16:10,220 --> 00:16:11,180
Where will you go then?

209
00:16:13,250 --> 00:16:14,610
I'll journey across the land

210
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:16,300
and resume my life
as a wandering physician.

211
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:20,130
Seriously?

212
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:21,850
I just got back,

213
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:23,490
and now you're leaving?

214
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,220
You have your life,

215
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:34,130
and I have mine.

216
00:16:34,770 --> 00:16:35,460
When you

217
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:36,820
visit Cailian

218
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:37,980
and Danxin's graves,

219
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:39,650
prepare an offering for me as well.

220
00:16:44,010 --> 00:16:44,940
What about Yuan Shaocheng?

221
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:46,300
Are you not going to tell him?

222
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:48,820
We merely crossed paths by chance.

223
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:51,890
When are you leaving?

224
00:16:52,530 --> 00:16:53,060
Today.

225
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,250
Why the rush?

226
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,650
The longer I wait,
the harder it is to say goodbye.

227
00:16:58,180 --> 00:16:59,060
It's better to be decisive.

228
00:17:01,250 --> 00:17:03,250
I've just written the song
"Late Coming Spring,"

229
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:04,980
and you haven't heard me sing it yet.

230
00:17:07,050 --> 00:17:08,570
Then do it now.

231
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:56,250
♪I see you ascend the tall tower alone♪

232
00:17:57,120 --> 00:18:02,370
♪You gaze eastward at your old home,
unaware of spring's arrival♪

233
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:11,020
♪Endless grass stretches
to the distant clouds at dusk♪

234
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:16,400
♪The wind sweeps through the pass
as half a lifetime slips away♪

235
00:18:18,970 --> 00:18:25,970
♪The hero's journey never ends♪

236
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:36,770
♪Do not forget those you've met
during the fleeting years♪

237
00:18:47,810 --> 00:18:48,460
When you

238
00:18:48,570 --> 00:18:49,770
visit Cailian

239
00:18:49,860 --> 00:18:51,010
and Danxin's graves,

240
00:18:51,290 --> 00:18:52,730
prepare an offering for me as well.

241
00:18:55,090 --> 00:18:56,090
Why the rush?

242
00:18:57,050 --> 00:18:58,460
The longer I wait,
the harder it is to say goodbye.

243
00:18:59,010 --> 00:18:59,900
It's better to be decisive.

244
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:14,290
She didn't even take
the calming incense.

245
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:23,290
That person looks familiar.

246
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:25,810
I think I've seen her
at Wanguoxiang Tavern before.

247
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:28,660
As long as you behave

248
00:19:29,050 --> 00:19:29,940
and treat Wanguoxiang Tavern

249
00:19:30,050 --> 00:19:31,290
as your own home,

250
00:19:31,730 --> 00:19:33,250
you'll be well-rewarded.

251
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:33,900
Now, keep up.

252
00:19:39,290 --> 00:19:40,220
Be careful.

253
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:41,860
Madame Hua

254
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:43,050
has recruited a new group of talents,

255
00:19:43,420 --> 00:19:44,500
all with unique abilities.

256
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:46,570
Why would she recruit people

257
00:19:47,050 --> 00:19:47,900
with unique talents?

258
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,050
You probably don't know this.

259
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:50,050
I've been here

260
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:51,290
longer than you.

261
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,460
Madame Hua

262
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:53,940
has a secret crew

263
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:55,020
who rarely

264
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:56,290
show themselves.

265
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:57,500
What do you mean by "secret crew?"

266
00:19:58,220 --> 00:19:59,730
This secret crew
is dedicated to catering

267
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:00,980
to the preferences
of influential figures.

268
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,770
Some are skilled in knife throwing,

269
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:03,810
fire-breathing performances,

270
00:20:04,180 --> 00:20:05,010
and even disguise techniques.

271
00:20:05,290 --> 00:20:06,260
Mastering these abilities

272
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:07,810
takes years of effort.

273
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:24,730
She said we merely crossed paths
by chance?

274
00:20:27,010 --> 00:20:27,980
That's not the point.

275
00:20:28,090 --> 00:20:29,330
She was perfectly fine before.

276
00:20:30,090 --> 00:20:30,730
Why did she

277
00:20:30,810 --> 00:20:32,090
suddenly decide to leave the capital

278
00:20:32,330 --> 00:20:33,330
after treating a woman?

279
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:35,220
I've seen that woman before.

280
00:20:35,490 --> 00:20:37,050
She's a new member
of the secret crew at Wanguoxiang.

281
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:38,460
I believe

282
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:39,530
Ping'an's departure

283
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:40,700
has something to do with her.

284
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,020
Do you know her name?

285
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:43,330
I don't,

286
00:20:43,730 --> 00:20:44,980
but she has a mole on her left cheek.

287
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:47,700
Wenyu.

288
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:50,770
